==English==
===Noun===
'''metazoan'''
#{{zoology}}: Any [[animal]] that undergoes [[development]] from an [[embryo]] stage with three [[tissue]] layers, namely the [[ectoderm]], [[mesoderm]], and [[endoderm]]. The term applies to all animals except the [[sponge]]s.

===Adjective===
'''metazoan'''
#Having to do with [[animal]]s that develop from an [[embryo]] with three [[tissue]] layers.

